The '''XP-21 groomer''' was a type of [[groomer]] eventually replaced by a more advanced model which had many more features and could be used for more purposes than [[Hair/Legends|haircare]]. [[Saun Dann]], a [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Merchant/Legends|merchant]] on [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]], sold such groomers to his [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] customers and he offered a newer model of groomer to an [[Unidentified Imperial guard|off-duty Imperial guard]] during the [[Blockade of Kashyyyk (1 ABY)|Blockade of Kashyyyk]]. Dann touted the functionality of the newer groomer model and informed the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] guard that the device could be plugged into any standard [[laser outlet]].<ref name="SWHS">''[[The Star Wars Holiday Special]]''</ref>

